Preparing for Marbles - Project plan

Starting date - 8/2 2010

Ending date - 9/7 2010

Total time: 22 weeks

Week 1 - Initial planning, making of this project plan, reading of articles
and other previously produced materials. Addressing of initial design issues
such as methods of dealing with multiple inheritance.

Week 2-4 - Further design and prototyping. Investigation into 'taxonomies'
of different formal devices involving trees, cf. Loek Cleophas thesis.

Week 5-10 - Definition and implementation of basic internal interfaces, basic
design work for the UI.

Week 10-15 - Implementation of concrete classes, building a simplistic GUI.

Week 16-22 - Wrapping up and writing a proper report
